{"tid":2140333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獲委任高院指定法官  周家明審國安法首案 被告申人身保護令","createTime":"2020-08-05T02:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T03:37:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"77e70e1725972e1ec858e2702f17ceb64a1083e6","tid":2140333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/USSSBXNIQ6NTKGOWFTP5JXMB3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FUSSSBXNIQ6NTKGOWFTP5JXMB3Y%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeah%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=77fc4233\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FUSSSBXNIQ6NTKGOWFTP5JXMB3Y%2F&h=42970ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/USSSBXNIQ6NTKGOWFTP5JXMB3Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n獲委任高院指定法官 <br />\n周家明審國安法首案 被告申人身保護令<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】23歲男子今年7.1駕駛插有「光復香港 時代革命」旗幟電單車，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HtM5tQLmOToBIpxjVnW546BTzJs=/190x142/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D5LZEJQOB4HCM5EUQSVZQXRTIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHtM5tQLmOToBIpxjVnW546BTzJs%3D%2F190x142%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD5LZEJQOB4HCM5EUQSVZQXRTIY.jpg&h=d0b42995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唐英傑透過律師向高院申請人身保護令。<br />\n<br />\n特首辦發言人回覆查詢，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n人身保護令案將於今天下午2時半開庭，申請人唐英傑（23歲）將由資深大律師戴啟思、大律師伍頴珊及黃瑞紅代表。協助申請人的律師行昨表示，國安法有不准保釋的推定，他們獲取的法律意見認為，循普通法申請人身保護令會較直接申請保釋容易。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LTLt6GDPgKnxG8TcaAxgGlrfndw=/190x237/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WTUPCTBEXWJ3UTMH346ZLFBOLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLTLt6GDPgKnxG8TcaAxgGlrfndw%3D%2F190x237%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWTUPCTBEXWJ3UTMH346ZLFBOLY.jpg&h=cf093ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周家明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大狀：若程序不當可申請<br />\n<br />\n唐早前在裁。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有大律師向本報指，羈押人士若被扣押時間過長或有關程序不當，可申請人身保護令要求釋放；例如。。。。。。。。。。。，保釋申請屬於人身保護令其中一個範疇，當正常法律途徑不適用時，才要動用人身保護令。<br />\n<br />\n大狀分析指，國安法假定嫌疑人不能保釋，除非該人能證明至法官相信他保釋期間不會繼續危害國家安全；但《基本法》及《香港人權法案》則是假定疑犯可獲保釋，除非該人有潛逃、再犯、或干擾證人的風險。大狀估計案件可能出現的爭拗點，是申請方會指國安法禁止保釋的規定違反人權法及違憲，律政司一方或會反駁有關限制是合符比例。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCAL1601、HCCP463/20"},{"pid":"83afba26da316e17c9c9d3cbb9a7cf274e157187","tid":2140333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T02:41:12.000Z","msg":"人身保護令案將於今天下午2時半開庭"},{"pid":"daabf1682f9a5a579f924f519e24e486d12b00cd","tid":2140333,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:13:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8917d7b024f7e50351f362b17bd2cd74d8ab6b34","tid":2140333,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb665eeb861484e3c07fec3b830566411e0c874","tid":2140333,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"戴啟思打，好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b231c616a1c2a0b073fc553448a30bee8076d18f","tid":2140333,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77e49988e4a4342fba44b3079313a6a688a64922","tid":2140333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"大家要捐612基金呀<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"0d06267ff1cdb4f929850617ebfcfbac7c9c2927","tid":2140333,"uid":174120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,